✨Happy Sunday! Today I pay tribute to @klemmusic @kevinlemons_highercalling. I had the pleasure of working with Kevin and his choir for a number of years. This footage is from a rehearsal for the @blackwalkoffame Black History month inductions performance with @sirthebaptist “Life Every Voice”. Kevin was extremely professional and a amazing musician.  To his family and love ones, I send my condolences. Forever grateful for your contribution to gospel music. Rest easy🕊️✨

✨When they go low I stand tall and high✨

#blackandproud #igetitfrommymomma #blessedandgrateful

✨Special delivery. Yesterday I received this fabulous invite from @marlohampton aka Lola for an event her @itsericathomas are hosting today honoring individuals who work in foster care. What was so sad for me was I learned that many children who are placed in homes are not given keys to the homes they are placed in. I am not saying this is the experience of all children but 1 is too many. I shared this only to bring light to this situation. Thank you Marlo and Erica for your work to bring awareness and resources around foster care.

#fortercare #ourkidsmatter #adopt #charrity #givingback #lovefaithhope

✨History was made on the last day of Black History month @blackwalkoffame induction. We inducted 3 iconic kings, @ambassadorandrewyoung @danny_glover_officail @dr._jones._ . I’m extremely happy that we were able to celebrate these incredible men for their contributions to the world. Each of them shared how important it is for all of us to find how we can each support our communities and those in need. They all shared incredible stories of overcoming challenges in their lives but always believed that the work they did was bigger than them. It was a call to action for all of us in that room. I will be sharing some of each one of their speeches later✨

#blackwalkoffame #blackhistorymonth #icons #andreyoung #dannyglover #bobbyjones #gec #bmac

Happy mother day mom! I’m so grateful that God chose you to be my mother. I miss you and often wonder what you are doing in heaven. I’m sure you are doing what you do best and that is praising with the the almighty. To all of the people who like me have lost their mothers. Let today and everyday be a celebration of love and  honor for our mothers who are not with us but are in us. Happy Mother’s Day to all of the incredible mothers!

Happy Mothers Day! Although I don’t have kids I take great pride in all of the kids we serve at @hopeforharvest_1 who are often abandoned by their parents. It take a village to raise our kids and we are a village to so many kids that come to our facility. To all of the women who are raising kids who are not your kids, blessings to you! May God grant you peace and blessings for your efforts. Thank you to our board and Hope partners for your support.

#happymothersday #hopeforharvest #godisgood #wecare #ourkidsmatter

✨I spent 2 days volunteering at @hopeforharvest_1 summer program. These 2 days were magical. I met so many amazing kids. This year we have a lot of kids under 12. This presented some different dynamics for the staff but they handled it all with such Grace. They are truly superheroes. Many of our kids are in difficult situations but the moment they walk through our doors, they are just kids at camp to learn, meet new friends and have some fun! Thank you @atljacob @kirkfranklin @kashdoll & @therealnictuc for FaceTime with the kids. You have no idea how much of an impact you had on the kids. To all of the staff and volunteers, the work you are doing will  have an indelible impact on every kid that we serve. A big thanks to the Charlotte fire department for hosting us. It was a big hit! Please follow @hopeforharvest_1 to learn more about our organization✨
